    <item>
      <title>台积电第二季度业绩或将推动其市值上涨 4200 亿美元，因人工智能需求飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/tsmc-s-second-quarter-results-may-fuel-its-420-billion-rally-as-ai-demand-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人工智能投资热潮不断超出预期，台积电今年 4,200 亿美元的市值涨幅可能会因另一季度强劲的盈利而进一步增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/tsmc-s-second-quarter-results-may-fuel-its-420-billion-rally-as-ai-demand-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:09:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称他需要更好地“控制自己的节奏”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/biden-says-he-needs-to-pace-himself-better-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他需要更好地“控制自己的节奏”，在下次辩论前不会出行太多。他在华盛顿的新闻发布会上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/biden-says-he-needs-to-pace-himself-better-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 00:18:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲最大另类资产管理公司考虑推出新中国基金，以扭转缩减开支的趋势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/pag-mulls-new-china-funds-as-pe-firm-bucks-retrenching-trend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，太盟集团正在设立一只中国基金以吸引国内资本，同时还在考虑设立另一只基金来满足北美以外投资者的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/pag-mulls-new-china-funds-as-pe-firm-bucks-retrenching-trend</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 00:03:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
